Class Nucleotide

java.lang.Object
  edu.udes.bio.genus.client.rna.Nucleotide
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Nucleotide
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Class Nucleotide. A nucleotide can be linked with up to 3 others nucleotides. 1- with the previous one in the structure. 2- with the next one in the structure. 3- with any other else in the structure.
